:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>At right-middle is th=
e name
of the selected ship or base. The name can be changed by typing a new one h=
ere.<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoNormal><span style=3D'mso-no-proof:yes'>Under the name is a s=
